---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="履歷 CV｜陳昱彰醫師 Dr. Yu-Chang Chen"
  description="陳昱彰醫師履歷。義大醫院家庭暨社區醫學部主治醫師、義大減重中心醫師。專長家庭醫學、肥胖醫學、運動醫學、職業醫學、行為科學。"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Person",
    "name": "陳昱彰",
    "alternateName": "Yu-Chang Chen",
    "jobTitle": "家庭醫學科主治醫師",
    "worksFor": [
      {
        "@type": "Hospital",
        "name": "義大醫院",
        "department": "家庭暨社區醫學部"
      },
      {
        "@type": "MedicalClinic", 
        "name": "義大減重中心"
      }
    ],
    "alumniOf": [
      {
        "@type": "CollegeOrUniversity",
        "name": "高雄醫學大學",
        "department": "醫學系"
      },
      {
        "@type": "CollegeOrUniversity",
        "name": "國立臺灣大學",
        "department": "公共衛生學院健康行為與社區科學研究所"
      }
    ],
    "knowsAbout": [
      "家庭醫學", "肥胖醫學", "運動醫學", "職業醫學", 
      "骨質疏鬆症", "行為科學", "實證醫學",
      "COM-B模型", "動機式晤談", "雙歷程理論"
    ],
    "url": "https://drcyc.io/cv",
    "sameAs": ["https://www.facebook.com/lazydr"],
    "email": "cyc@edfm.org"
  })} />

  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="container nav-inner">
      <a href="/" class="nav-brand">YC Chen, MD</a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/">首頁</a>
        <a href="/workplace-health">臨場服務</a>
        <a href="/health-checkup">高階健檢</a>
        <a href="/community-health">社區營造</a>
        <a href="/cv">CV</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>履歷 Curriculum Vitae</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container cv-container">
      
      <div class="cv-header">
        <img src="/images/portrait.jpg" alt="陳昱彰醫師" class="cv-photo" />
        <div class="cv-intro">
          <h2>陳昱彰 <span class="en-name">Yu-Chang Chen, MD</span></h2>
          <p class="cv-title">家庭醫學科主治醫師</p>
          <p class="cv-tagline">行為科學 × 臨床醫學</p>
          <div class="cv-contact">
            <span>📧 <a href="mailto:cyc@edfm.org">cyc@edfm.org</a></span>
            <span>🌐 <a href="https://drcyc.io">drcyc.io</a></span>
            <span>📱 <a href="https://facebook.com/lazydr" target="_blank">FB @lazydr</a></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cv-section">
        <h3>🏥 現職</h3>
        <ul class="cv-list">
          <li>
            <strong>義大醫院 家庭暨社區醫學部</strong> — 主治醫師
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>義大減重中心</strong> — 醫師
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>職業醫學科</strong> — 訓練醫師
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="cv-section">
        <h3>🎓 學歷</h3>
        <ul class="cv-list">
          <li>
            <strong>國立臺灣大學 公共衛生學院</strong><br/>
            <span class="cv-detail">健康行為與社區科學研究所（研修）</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>高雄醫學大學</strong><br/>
            <span class="cv-detail">醫學系 畢業</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="cv-section">
        <h3>🩺 專長領域</h3>
        <div class="cv-tags">
          <span class="tag">家庭醫學</span>
          <span class="tag">肥胖醫學</span>
          <span class="tag">運動醫學</span>
          <span class="tag">職業醫學</span>
          <span class="tag">骨質疏鬆症</span>
          <span class="tag">行為科學</span>
          <span class="tag">實證醫學</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cv-section">
        <h3>🧠 行為科學專長</h3>
        <div class="cv-tags">
          <span class="tag">COM-B 行為改變模型</span>
          <span class="tag">動機式晤談 (MI)</span>
          <span class="tag">雙歷程理論</span>
          <span class="tag">健康行為介入設計</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cv-section">
        <h3>💼 服務項目</h3>
        <ul class="cv-list">
          <li>慢性病管理（糖尿病、高血壓、高血脂）</li>
          <li>肥胖醫學與個人化減重門診</li>
          <li>運動醫學與運動處方設計</li>
          <li>企業臨場健康服務</li>
          <li>骨質疏鬆評估與治療</li>
          <li>高階健康檢查</li>
          <li>社區健康營造</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="cv-section">
        <h3>💡 臨床理念</h3>
        <blockquote class="cv-quote">
          「醫學的價值，不僅在於治療疾病，更在於幫助人們過上更好的生活。」
        </blockquote>
        <p>
          以「<strong>理解 → 溝通 → 改變</strong>」三步驟為核心，
          將行為科學系統性導入臨床實踐，
          協助患者建立可持續的健康行為改變。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="cv-section">
        <h3>🎯 興趣</h3>
        <div class="cv-tags">
          <span class="tag">圍棋</span>
          <span class="tag">馬拉松</span>
          <span class="tag">健身</span>
          <span class="tag">烏克麗麗</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 
      待補充區塊（請提供資料）：
      
      <div class="cv-section">
        <h3>📜 證照</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="cv-section">
        <h3>📚 著作/發表</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="cv-section">
        <h3>🏆 獎項/榮譽</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="cv-section">
        <h3>🎤 演講/授課</h3>
      </div>
      -->

    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <p>© 2026 陳昱彰醫師｜守護健康，從理解與溝通開始。</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  .nav { position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.95);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); }
  .nav-inner { display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:64px; }
  .nav-brand { font-weight:700;font-size:1.15rem;color:var(--text); }
  .nav-brand:hover { text-decoration:none; }
  .nav-links { display:flex;gap:1.5rem; }
  .nav-links a { color:var(--text-light);font-size:0.95rem; }
  .nav-links a:hover { color:var(--primary);text-decoration:none; }

  .page-hero { padding:4rem 0 2rem;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f0f5ff 0%,#e8f0fe 100%);text-align:center; }
  .page-hero h1 { font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800; }

  .section { padding:3rem 0 5rem; }
  
  .cv-container { max-width:800px;margin:0 auto; }
  
  .cv-header {
    display:flex;gap:2rem;align-items:center;
    padding:2rem;background:var(--bg-light);border-radius:var(--radius);
    margin-bottom:2rem;
  }
  .cv-photo {
    width:150px;height:180px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:var(--radius);
    box-shadow:0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  .cv-intro h2 { font-size:1.8rem;margin-bottom:0.25rem; }
  .en-name { font-weight:400;color:var(--text-light);font-size:1.2rem; }
  .cv-title { font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--primary);font-weight:600;margin-bottom:0.25rem; }
  .cv-tagline { color:var(--text-light);margin-bottom:1rem; }
  .cv-contact { display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1rem;font-size:0.9rem; }
  .cv-contact a { color:var(--primary); }

  .cv-section { margin-bottom:2.5rem; }
  .cv-section h3 { font-size:1.3rem;margin-bottom:1rem;padding-bottom:0.5rem;border-bottom:2px solid var(--border); }
  
  .cv-list { list-style:none;padding:0; }
  .cv-list li { margin-bottom:0.75rem;padding-left:1rem;position:relative; }
  .cv-list li::before { content:"•";position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--primary); }
  .cv-detail { color:var(--text-light);font-size:0.95rem; }

  .cv-tags { display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.5rem; }
  .tag {
    background:var(--bg-light);border:1px solid var(--border);
    padding:0.35rem 0.75rem;border-radius:99px;font-size:0.9rem;
  }

  .cv-quote {
    border-left:4px solid var(--primary);padding:1rem 1.5rem;
    margin:0 0 1rem 0;font-style:italic;background:var(--bg-light);
    border-radius:0 var(--radius) var(--radius) 0;
  }

  .footer { padding:2rem 0;text-align:center;color:var(--text-light);font-size:0.9rem;border-top:1px solid var(--border); }

  @media (max-width:640px) {
    .cv-header { flex-direction:column;text-align:center; }
    .cv-contact { justify-content:center; }
    .page-hero h1 { font-size:2rem; }
  }
</style>
